## Project Attribution

This project is a fork of [Microsoft SimpleChat](https://github.com/microsoft/simplechat),
extended with Azure NetApp Files integration for enterprise AI workloads.

### Parent Repository
- **Name:** SimpleChat
- **Owner:** Microsoft Corporation
- **URL:** https://github.com/microsoft/simplechat
- **License:** MIT

### This Fork
- **Name:** SimpleChat-ANF
- **Purpose:** Demonstrate Azure NetApp Files as enterprise storage for AI/RAG workloads
- **Integration:** Azure NetApp Files Object REST API, NFS, SMB protocols

## Disclaimer

This software is provided for demonstration and educational purposes. The authors
and contributors make no warranties regarding the suitability of this software
for production use.

- Azure NetApp Files Object REST API is currently in PREVIEW
- Users are responsible for their own Azure resource costs
- Users are responsible for security configuration and compliance
- This project is not officially supported by Microsoft or NetApp

For production deployments, please consult the official documentation:
- [Azure NetApp Files](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-netapp-files/)
- [Microsoft SimpleChat](https://github.com/microsoft/simplechat)

